$lang['This number system uses 16 symbols that are represented in a range from 0-9 or A-F. The 0–9 represent numbers up to nine whereas A-F is represented by the numeric 10–15. As compared to the other three types of number systems, the hexadecimal numeral system is considered to be the most effective one.'] = '該數字系統使用 16 個符號，以 0-9 或 AF 的範圍表示。 0-9 代表最多 9 個數字，而 AF 由數字 10-15 代表。 與其他三種數字系統相比，十六進制數字系統被認為是最有效的一種。';
